Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.83,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,W-We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.17,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,We finally got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:28.21,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,It's been lost for a hundred years, but now the treasure is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:30.00,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,All right, careful now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:33.63,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Keep calm! Just bring it this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.63,Secondary,Sailors,0,0,0,,I got it! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:34.51,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Up we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:37.93,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Isn't it a bit long for a treasure chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:40.10,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Hey! You're lifting it too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.14,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm setting it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.27,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:48.90,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Yes! Pry it open, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:50.78,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Wait. How bizarre...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:54.03,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,This box is locked from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:56.53,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Who gives a shit? Bust it open!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:58.95,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,H-Hold on! There's something engraved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:02.91,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,D-I-O... Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:04.21,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Is it a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.67,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Do you think anyone gives a damn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:08.54,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,The sun is about to set!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:10.96,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Once it gets dark, it'll be impossible to see how to get it open!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:12.63,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Yeah, good point!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.67,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Right! Let me go grab the blowtorch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:17.80,Main,Sailors,0,0,0,,Get ready to say hello to treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:24.31,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,One day, an unmanned cruiser was sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:28.98,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The boat was in perfect working order, \Nand there was no indication of an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:33.94,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only signs of life on board \Nwere three half-full cups of coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:35.24,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:41.83,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,An acetylene blowtorch.\N It had been used to open the steel box on deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:48.58,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The box was empty, but it is believed to have\N sheltered something inside its two compartments.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:55.84,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Some believed it contained treasure, \Nbut after a few months, it was entirely forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:04.52,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Kujo Jotaro, Seventeen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:07.10,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Height: 195 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:10.23,Main,Police,0,0,0,,His father is a Japanese jazz musician.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.44,Main,Police,0,0,0,,He's currently on tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:15.99,Main,Police,0,0,0,,His mother is an American of British descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:19.99,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,That's him. Jotaro is my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:22.91,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Apparently his friends at school took the "Jo" from Kujo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:26.79,Main,Police,0,0,0,,...and the "Jo" from Jotaro to nickname him Jojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:28.87,Main,Police,0,0,0,,What a riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:31.17,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,S-So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:34.17,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,How many people did Jotaro kill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:39.05,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Don't tell me! I don't want to hear it! No! {This line should be retimed to start after the "Kyaa!" since I assume we aren't subbing that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:39.05,Secondary,Police,0,0,0,,Uh, who told you he killed anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.55,Main,Police,0,0,0,,He just got into a little scrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:44.89,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Actually, the thugs he faced were armed with nunchucks and knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:49.73,Main,Police,0,0,0,,There were four of them, including a former boxer, \Nand your son managed to break fifteen bones between them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.60,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Their balls were crushed and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:54.65,Main,Police,0,0,0,,...Pardon my language...\N They were sent to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:58.15,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Ma'am, please make sure he learns his lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.40,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.66,Main,Police,0,0,0,,But the real problem is what happened after.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.37,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Could you copy this and pass it around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.28,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.66,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Your son is quite the oddball.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.00,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Come in. We'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.25,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.63,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, please take him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.76,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,What? He's being released already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:20.38,Main,Police,0,0,0,,We can't keep him forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:25.01,Main,Police,0,0,0,,By the way, ma'am, your Japanese is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.27,Main,Police,0,0,0,,How long have you lived in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.56,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.27,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Ah, no wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.73,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:34.31,Main,Police,0,0,0,,We've had our hands full lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.73,Main,Police,0,0,0,,There's even a waiting list for our cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.74,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Your son is just up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.53,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.83,Flashback,Holly,0,0,0,,Jotaro, throw the ball to Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.08,Flashback,Holly,0,0,0,,Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.54,Flashback,Holly,0,0,0,,Do your best at the sports meet tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.58,Flashback,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.17,Thoughts,Holly,0,0,0,,Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.05,Flashback,Holly,0,0,0,,We should celebrate.\N What would you like to eat today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.30,Flashback,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Mom, all I want is to eat your cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:06.47,Thoughts,Holly,0,0,0,,Jotaro... Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.39,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:10.73,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.81,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Don't be such a pain, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.27,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.95,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,He's actually a very sweet child!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.99,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,He would never do something so awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.12,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't fall asleep, Kujo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.66,Main,Police,0,0,0,,You're being released. Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:35.00,Main,Police,0,0,0,,What part of "go home" don't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:45.22,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Mom, go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.97,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'll be hanging out here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:51.14,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I've been possessed by an evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.94,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I have no idea what it could make me do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:58.06,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Even during that fight, it took all I had to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.61,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,So you better not let me out of this cell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:05.07,Main,Police,0,0,0,,For crying out loud, Ma'am! Do you see what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:08.24,Main,Police,0,0,0,,We're trying to release him, but he refuses to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:13.45,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Forgive my asking, but is your son well in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.04,Main,Police,0,0,0,,This isn't some hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.04,Main,Inmates,0,0,0,,Please! Let us change cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.71,Main,Inmates,0,0,0,,He's telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:22.00,Main,Inmates,0,0,0,,There really is an evil spirit possessing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.67,Secondary,Inmates,0,0,0,,It's terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:25.59,Main,Inmates,0,0,0,,We'll never do bad things again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.59,Secondary,Police,0,0,0,,That's enough! Quiet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.48,Main,Police,0,0,0,,W-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:39.19,Main,Police,0,0,0,,You're behind bars! \NHow the hell did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:43.90,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:46.03,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,It's the evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:48.16,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,The evil spirit brings things to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:53.58,Main,Police,0,0,0,,H-He's reading Shounen Jump while listening to his boombox!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:56.00,Main,Police,0,0,0,,H-How?! Th-This ain't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:56.96,Main,Police,0,0,0,,This isn't good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:57.79,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:02.88,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I doubt this will be enough to stop you from releasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.38,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'll show you just how frightening the evil spirit can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:10.09,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Then maybe you'll understand why it's such a bad idea to let me loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:25.36,Main,Police,0,0,0,,H-He took my gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.86,Main,Police,0,0,0,,W-We've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:31.62,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Hey officers, did you finally see it? That's the evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.62,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,If you didn't, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.29,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,J-Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.51,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,There's something behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.06,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,It must have just recently possessed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:59.56,Thoughts,Holly,0,0,0,,His grandfather, Joseph, has strange powers, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:03.44,Thoughts,Holly,0,0,0,,W-What's happening to my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:16.87,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.87,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Over here, Papa! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.71,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Holly! Hey, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.04,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.17,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.13,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.63,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,If my only daughter needs my help...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:32.59,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I can be anywhere in the world within 24 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:34.85,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Where's Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.60,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,She complained...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:41.39,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,But I told Suzi it was a business trip\N for the Joestar real estate agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:43.94,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:48.07,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Holly... Holly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.69,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Hey, Holly! Get off me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:54.74,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,No! It's been forever since you last held me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.12,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Look, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.75,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,How can a 45 year-old woman talk like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.50,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Oh, now you've done it! It's tickling time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.33,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Hey! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.51,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,What the hell are you people gawking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:11.84,Main,Confused Child,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:11.84,Secondary,Perturbed Mother,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.22,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,I'll take your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:16.35,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,By the way, Holly, about Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.85,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,You're certain he said "evil spirit"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.56,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,What's happened to you, Jotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:28.65,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,That's right. The policemen said they couldn't see it, but I saw it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.19,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,I saw a separate arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:31.99,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,And it grabbed the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:35.49,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,The others couldn't see it, but you could?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:36.70,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:41.75,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,So Jotaro says that he's been possessed recently,\N but nothing strange has happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:47.83,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Not to me. But Jotaro says he won't leave the cell \Nuntil he knows what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.38,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Papa, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.63,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,There, there, my beloved daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:55.34,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about when Joseph Joestar is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.05,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.31,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up and see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:06.06,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,My grandson, Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.62,Main,Inmates,0,0,0,,H-How terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.58,Main,Inmates,0,0,0,,That thing brought him even more stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.70,Main,Inmates,0,0,0,,And it's violent...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.41,Main,Inmates,0,0,0,,That thing possessing him is horrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:30.71,Main,Police,0,0,0,,I-If the general public caught wind of this, \NI'd lose my job in a heartbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:34.59,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll be taking my grandson home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:35.92,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,"Grandson"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.68,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:41.05,Main,Police,0,0,0,,I told you, this is as far as you'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:43.47,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Convince him from over here! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.81,Secondary,Joseph,0,0,0,,It's fine, now move it! Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:46.23,Main,Police,0,0,0,,We can't be held responsible for this! Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.23,Secondary,Joseph,0,0,0,,Hey, outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.19,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Jotaro! It's your grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.73,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll be able to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.07,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Please come out with your grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.29,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Get out. We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.25,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.92,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Nobody asked you to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:15.59,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,You think you'll help me? What the hell can {\i1}you{\i0} do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:20.34,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Sorry you got dragged here all the way from New York,\N but you won't be able to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:26.77,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,Th-The pinky from my prosthetic hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.27,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,When did he take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.65,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,You see? Do you finally get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:35.32,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,It's the evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.40,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Don't get too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.82,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,You'll only shorten the little life you have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:44.41,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,H-How can this be? I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:47.20,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,It was able to deceive me right off the bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:52.46,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,Yes... I know exactly what Jotaro's evil spirit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:57.30,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,But rather than explaining it with words, \Nif I make him experience the truth himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.76,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,...he'll get a better grasp of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:02.55,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,No, the real reason he needs to physically understand it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.72,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,...is to face the dangers that lie ahead for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.18,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Abdul, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:13.02,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,This is my friend of three years from Egypt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.15,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Abdul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:21.78,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Force my grandson Jotaro out of this cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.53,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Don't even try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:30.12,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,He looks strong, but do you really think I'd let \Nsomeone force me out of here just because you said so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.29,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,No way in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:36.29,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'll just want to stay even longer if he tries to force me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.46,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,This will require a bit of violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:45.01,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,Soon enough he will be in such pain, \Nhe will squeal, "Please get me out of here."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.39,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:47.81,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Papa, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.52,Main,Police,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you can't{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.68,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:51.64,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:09.54,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:15.25,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Yes, Abdul also has a so-called "evil spirit."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:18.17,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,An evil spirit he can freely control!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.63,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,The evil spirit's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:22.92,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Magician's Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:33.10,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I-It's hot! The fire! I'm burning!\N My arms are burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.31,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,W-What is this evil spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:39.07,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Kujo's thrown himself against the wall and won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.07,Main,Police,0,0,0,,This doesn't make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:43.28,Main,Police,0,0,0,,A-And isn't it getting a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.78,Main,Police,0,0,0,,How is it that hot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.95,Main,Police,0,0,0,,That's insane! It's way too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:57.21,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Oh, there it is! It's finally revealed itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:13:02.21,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,And the fact that it's so clearly visible means it's very powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.01,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:13.23,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,I cannot believe he is able to manifest it so vividly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:15.89,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you got an evil spirit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:19.86,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,And Gramps, the identity of the evil spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.61,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I know of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:26.28,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar, you asked me to get your grandson out of the cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:28.57,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,I was planning on holding back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:32.37,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,...but we are in grave danger from how strong it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.20,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,Shall I stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:42.09,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,If you continue to insist I get him out, it will require using enough force to send your grandson to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:44.34,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,So be it. Give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.84,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.64,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,Red Bind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:52.18,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:59.19,Main,Police,0,0,0,,There's so much heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.82,Main,Police,0,0,0,,I don't have a clue what's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.69,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Papa! What are you doing to Jotaro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:08.20,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Holly, be a good girl and keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:08.91,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.66,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I-I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.33,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,The evil spirit's withdrawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:17.87,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,If your breathing is restricted, your evil spirit will weaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.92,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.79,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Despite appearances, it is not an evil spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:30.30,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Jotaro, what you believed was an evil spirit is actually a being created from your life energy; a kind of powerful vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:35.56,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Because it stands beside you, we have a special name for this vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.10,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,A Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.19,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,A Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.02,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,As it is told in Aesop's Fables...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:47.99,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,The cold wind only made the traveler pull his coat on tight, \Nbut the heat made him admit defeat. {Abdul is referencing the fable "The North Wind and The Sun." You can read it here: https://www.storyarts.org/library/aesops/stories/north.html}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:50.66,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,Do you want to come out of your cell now, Jojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.41,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Enough of this shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:59.83,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,The reason I refuse to leave is because \NI keep harming others without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.38,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,It's interesting you got an evil spirit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.42,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,But if you keep doing this shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.17,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.68,Main,Police,0,0,0,,He smashed the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.93,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Th-That's destruction of property!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.90,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.57,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.82,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Don't say I didn't warn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:45.46,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:47.96,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Why'd you suddenly turn your back on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.21,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Turn and face me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.76,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:56.01,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,As you can see, I have forced him from the cell, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.27,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Are you saying you let me win?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:09.53,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:15.16,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,It truly was my intent to send you to the hospital, \Nbut I did not expect you to be so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:20.33,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,If I hadn't stopped this steel rod, what would you have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:23.67,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,My Stand is Magician's Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:27.71,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,It could melt a steel rod like this in midair with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:31.01,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Abdul has the same power as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:38.05,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,You don't need to stay in that cell to\N research your evil spirit any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:49.98,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:53.03,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Jotaro finally came out of his cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.57,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,You're such a pain, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.61,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.62,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Hey, you punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:01.75,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,How dare you speak to your mother like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.96,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,And Holly, don't smile after he insults you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.37,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.54,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gramps, just one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:11.09,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,There's just one thing I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:17.01,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Why did you know about my evil spirit... \Nno... my Stand or whatever it's called?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.51,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,That's what I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:21.51,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:24.60,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I came here from New York to let you know what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:29.40,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,But to properly explain it, I must start from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:32.11,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It has to do with the Joestar family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.74,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Take a look at these pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.49,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:46.75,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It's a one-hundred-year-old coffin, pulled up from \Nthe Atlantic Ocean off the coast of Africa four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:47.75,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Coffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.71,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I did some research after it came into my possession...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:59.64,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I discovered that four generations before you, my grandfather, \NJonathan Joestar, died on the ship where this coffin was hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:04.60,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Apparently it was empty by the time they discovered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.35,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,But I know exactly what was inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:10.61,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Abdul and I are trying to discover where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:12.77,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,He? Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:16.28,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,"He" makes it sound like you're talking about a living person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:19.86,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,How could something lost at sea for a hundred years be alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.03,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Because he is evil incarnate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:24.29,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,His name is Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:27.00,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,He has awoken from his hundred-year sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:30.54,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It is our fate to do battle with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.05,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,The hell was that, Jotaro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:38.42,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Don't give me that face like this has nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:43.05,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,This face means,\N "That was so stupid, I don't know what to say," old timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.35,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,O-Old timer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.81,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Abdul, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:50.52,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,We just met, but you act like you're above me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.06,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,And Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:56.23,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Do you expect me to eat up an unbelievable story like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:04.99,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,But would you not have found that our evil spirits are equally as unbelievable?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.29,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:09.91,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, you'll have to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:15.30,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,If you're curious how I know of Dio's existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:17.96,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,...and why exactly I'm going after him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.22,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:27.35,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Actually, about a year ago, I also suddenly obtained an evil spirit, or rather, the power of a Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:28.60,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.19,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gramps, what did you{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:34.81,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'll show you! My Stand's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:36.57,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,...powerful ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:45.66,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.58,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,The thorns that came from my hand? That was my Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:52.79,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It has the powerful ability to take spirit photos of visions I've captured from far away places!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:57.55,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Though every time I do it, I have to destroy a 30,000 yen camera in the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.59,Main,Waiter,0,0,0,,Good sir, is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.76,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,It is fine. Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:03.80,Main,Waiter,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:08.31,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,The vision that will appear in this picture, Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:11.64,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,...will be what determines your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:12.81,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:18.94,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Jotaro, Holly... Have either of you ever taken a close look at the back of your necks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:20.94,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,What are you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:24.95,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I doubt you've ever bothered to look closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:29.62,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,...but right around the base of my neck, \Nthere is a star-shaped birthmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:35.38,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Again, what the fuck are you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:41.26,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I asked my mother about it, and she said that my father,\N who died when I was young, also had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:46.39,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Apparently those belonging to the Joestar bloodline\N all have this star-shaped birthmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.85,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Hey, Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:50.35,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,What the hell is gonna show up on that film?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:53.94,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,This is our undiscovered destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:58.15,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Dammit, just show me what the hell is on it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:55.10,Secondary,Holly,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:05.11,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:08.16,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,He has consistently shown up on all of my spirit photos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.66,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,And on the back of his neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.12,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,From this asshole's neck down...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:18.29,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,...is the body of my grandfather, Jonathan Joestar, \Nwhich he's doing hell knows what with!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.76,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,A hundred years ago,\N there was an incident on the Atlantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:27.34,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,My grandmother Erina is the one who told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:31.56,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,But needless to say, Dio took possession of my grandfather's body and survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:33.89,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,And there's one thing I'm certain of...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:38.98,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,That son of bitch is hiding somewhere around the world, plotting something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:41.44,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It was four years ago that he returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:49.57,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,The reason my spirit photos and your evil spirit \Nbegan to manifest this past year... is most certainly related to Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:53.24,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,In the wider world, our gifts are considered psychic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:56.29,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,My Stand has been with me since birth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.17,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,...but your powers are linked to Dio's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:03.80,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,So in effect, you are linked to Jonathan's body by invisible threads.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:09.26,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,All that we know for certain is that it was Dio's existence that brought forth this dormant power within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:14.52,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Abdul, can you tell where he is from this photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:19.60,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,I cannot. The background is hardly discernible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:21.48,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:23.40,Main,Abdul,0,0,0,,I shall give it a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:24.78,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'm counting on{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:27.90,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Oh, Holly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:30.53,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I had to bring this up all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:31.95,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Now, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.95,0:22:32.91,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:36.00,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be visiting Japan for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:38.08,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I'll be staying at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:39.71,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Yes, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:41.58,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Jotaro, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:56.56,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:23:02.40,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Just now, it felt as if something was observing me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:05.94,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Is it Jonathan's descendants, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:10.95,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This body must be sending out some kind of message through his soul to his descendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:15.79,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Very well. Is this what they call "fate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:17.70,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,It is a fate I must be rid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:20.21,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,A destiny I must erase.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:23.29,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I have already made my move.
