Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:29.47,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:32.05,Main,Holly,0,0,0,,Here, a goodbye kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:34.55,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Dammit, woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:34.55,Secondary,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Kakyoin Noriaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:38.85,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I just transferred here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:38.85,Secondary,Nurse,0,0,0,,Does this look like a fucking pen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:41.35,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,The loser is the evil one.
